Two violent convicts on the run from an open prison have been found, police have confirmed.

The 'Scarborough Slasher' Damien Burns, 39, and thief Dean Jackson, 27, escaped from HMP Hatfield, a Category D prison in Doncaster, South Yorkshire, on Monday night.

Police warned the public not to approach either of the men.

